{"4219400": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "璀璨時刻～與女同事曖昧不清的親密關係～", "steam_appid": 4219400, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Story</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >璀璨時刻是一款選擇導向的視覺小說遊戲，在遊戲中你扮演不僅感情被綠，工作又突然出現急件的IT人員，公司還安排你與頂尖工程師「黃金」與實力派新人「Ruby」一起完成專案。在這最後一個月中你也漸漸與他們發展出預期外的關係</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4219400/extras/e970610239aeb730908ad0de098bb25c.avif?t=1771491935\" width=1560 height=878 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4219400/extras/c45a3ec97bcfbb264576481c437aa63c.avif?t=1771491935\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Character</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>黃金</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主角的組長，外表冷淡看起來總是睡眠不足。公司中的程式大神。因「知識就是黃金」而被公司的人稱作黃金。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4219400/extras/17e9dc9c9cd847c0b2b9cc3e44b6ed5e.avif?t=1771491935\" width=300 height=600 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Ruby</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在主角接到緊急專案後加入的新人，自稱「新人的Ruby」。觀察力強、節儉、行事果決、因為身材有點堤防異性。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4219400/extras/0643ab3e150417e2cec4d509453dbd17.avif?t=1771491935\" width=300 height=600 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Feature</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >選擇導向視覺小說，讓遊戲不只一個結局</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragrap